title: Breville -- Baking Craft: Amaretti Cookie
description:
For more about Breville products visit: www.brevilleusa.com

Adele Schober speaks to Mellisa Kelly Chef and Owner Of Primo Restaurant in Main. They talk about how convenient the Breville Stand Mixer is to make her Amaretti Cookie and all her food is made from scratch.
